00056 #define __MIN_ASSERT_SHARED(__assertion__, __aMessage__) \
00057 if(!__assertion__) { \
00058                 min_debug(__FUNCTION__, __LINE__,__FILE__, __aMessage__);\
00059                 RESULT(__result__,TP_FAILED,__aMessage__);\
00060 }
00061 
00062 #define __MIN_ASSERT_SHARED_DESC(__assertion__, __aMessage__, __aDesc__) \
00063 if(!__assertion__) { \
00064                 min_debug(__FUNCTION__, __LINE__,__FILE__, __aMessage__);\
00065                 RESULT2(__result__,TP_FAILED,__aMessage__, __aDesc__);\
00066 }
